reviews.text: Just walked into this really nice local restaurant. Very busy with local people. Their specialty is pork apparently and the pork skin very crispy and rice underneath the pork meat. We didn’t order the whole pig as it would serve a group of 5-10. Small portion was just perfect for me and my friend. I would go back again and recommend my friends.
Price is cheap, but the environment is dirty. Food is acceptable.
Seems the food less delicious then before

result.name: 季季紅

reviews.text: Just walked into this really nice local restaurant. Very busy with local people. Their specialty is pork apparently and the pork skin very crispy and rice underneath the pork meat. We didn’t order the whole pig as it would serve a group of 5-10. Small portion was just perfect for me and my friend. I would go back again and recommend my friends.
一間以豬仔糯米飯出名，服務一般，除出名豬仔飯外，無甚可取，小菜做得麻麻，待應越叫越走，我地一行16人，光顧四次，每次都令人失望，有次常試叫小菜，因套餐都是差不多一樣的餸菜，但待應們即面口不同(更差)，老實講，由於人多，每次安排的位置都會唔夠坐，但可以理解，是否係服務同食物方面，提升少許呢！希望日後有所改善啦！
荃灣呢個店出品有米乳猪比蓝地老店好，值得各位去試。
地點就腳，裝修不奢華， 晚上七時半不用等位，還有空枱，食物和價錢合理，服務態度可以，埋咗單就開始催你走人，令老人家不高興😓
